data.description: Beautiful 2 bedroom 2 bath home on 44.5 acres. Open concept floor plan with custom red oak cabinets, breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Large master suite with a walk-in closet and master bathroom with dual vanities and tile shower. Tile floors in both bathrooms and gorgeous bamboo flooring throughout the remainder of the home. Adjacent to the home is a 30x40 metal shop with a tack room and climate controlled office. The shop has a 4 car carport on the front and 2 horse stalls on the back. Also on the property is an 80x40 cattle barn with feed lot and pond. Property has several large pecan trees and highway frontage.
